#: ../../user-manual/add-edit-content/authority-records.rst:579
msgid ""
"The International Council on Archives' :ref:`ISAD(G) <isad-template>` "
"standard defines an :term:`access point` as a \"*name, term, keyword, phrase"
" or code that may be used to search, identify and locate an archival "
"description.*\" Access points help users not only understand contextual "
"information, but discover further related content. In AtoM, you can now "
"apply access points to an :term:`authority record` as well."
